pets.desc: Belle (Beagle) and Maverick (Pomsky) are the dogs of the couple. They have been best friends since they met when they were just puppies.
Angel was the Brides cat before she met the Groom. However, Angel quickly warmed up to the Groom and he is now, without a doubt, Angel's favorite human.

proposal.desc: Darby proposed to Caitlyn in Halmstad, Sweden with Maverick in attendance.

misc.desc: Caitlyn and Darby together at Faster Horses!
The Bride and Groom enjoy activities like axe throwing in their off time!
In the off season, the Bride and Groom love to travel and go to Tigers games! Go Tigers!
Caitlyn and Darby at Caitlyn's graduation. Always supporting each other!
